Note
Try to achieve the Layout as close as possible.
Warning
Always place the columns inside a row, even if it's within an existing column.

Example
Wrong Usage

<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-6">
        Main Column
            <div class="col-6">Column 1</div>
            <div class="col-6">Column 2</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
 
HTML
Correct Usage

<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-6">
        Main Column
            <div class="col-6">Column 1</div>
            <div class="col-6">Column 2</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
  
HTML
